Overall, the acceptability of vaccines is a complex process that can be affected by several factors. Regarding the decision to vaccinate, in 2014, the Strategic Advisory Group of Experts (SAGE) sought to understand the determinant factors of vaccination99. Appendices to the report of the Sage Working Group on Vaccine Hesitancy [Internet]. 2014 [cited 2014 Apr 22]. Available from: Available from: https://www.comminit.com/polio/content/appendices-report-sage-working-group-vaccine-hesitancy
